
   =========================================================
   |                                                       |
   |   CBGB - Common Block harvester for GAMBIT Backends   |
   |                                                       |
   =========================================================

To use CBGB:

  1. Set configurations in modules/cfg.py 

  2. Execute ./cbgb.py

  3. Copy the generated code needed for GAMBIT from the following output files: 

       backend_types_header_code.hpp, frontent_header_code.hpp
